Measurements were performed at axial exp.channel
of cylindrical core. Besides U-235 the reactor
Critical assembly( no details) was used .
Spectrum approximation were - Watt spectrum (in DOC),
Cranberg spectrum (in DOC), Maxwellian spectrum (in AE
and DOC ). Below 3 MeV the reactor spectrum differs
from the fission spectrum. Above 3 MeV spectra are
Spectrum of energy range 0.6-24 MeV within U reactor.
Average energy of reactor neutrons was 1.42+-0.04 MeV.

The neutron flux in the channel was measured
